{"pageProps":{"post":{"mdxSource":"<img src=\"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1carw3h2j30vy0dwqga.jpg\" />\n\n<h1>2D物理节点调整</h1>\n<p>物理插值用于分离物理刻度和显示帧速率。它会在上一个物理位置和当前物理位置之间创建额外的帧。这减少了抖动，有效地使整体外观更加平滑。</p>\n<p>这对两件事很有用：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>您的游戏在高刷新率的显示器上看起来会更好</li>\n<li>如果您正在制作手机游戏，较低的节拍率对您开发的硬件的负担较小，但通常意味着会牺牲流畅度。现在不是了！</li>\n</ul>\n","frontMatter":{"readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","minutes":0.78,"time":46800,"words":156},"slug":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-2D物理特性调整","fileName":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-2D物理特性调整.md","date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1carw3h2j30vy0dwqga.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"godot4.3-2D物理特性调整"}},"prev":{"date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1cevoz60j30wy0e6166.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"godot4.3-关于多线程性能模型的调整","slug":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-关于多线程性能模型的调整"},"next":null},"__N_SSG":true}